The paper deals with image classification and retrieval in digital pathology, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of machine learning algorithms such as LBP, dictionary approach, and CNNs suggests that the paper may also fall under sub-categories such as information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), and deep learning (cs.DL).
